{"tid":1373183,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母可唔可以揾次真係支持返前線嘅決定","createTime":"2019-07-27T14:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T00:09:19.000Z","uid":32382,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d885178e5c40877d826384074bda8daa9bae7179","tid":1373183,"uid":32382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:48:02.000Z","msg":"次撚次差唔多時間就有人話走<br />\n前線多數都唔係幾想走架啦<br />\n但啲人就會去後面同和理非講前線決定左幾多點走<br />\n然後去到嗰個時間前線就發現後面冇撚哂人<br />\n然後焗住要退<br />\n真係話冇鬼都冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前線決定左幾時走夠鐘就自然會叫後面退架啦屌<br />\n721上環又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29a8c601d736ccf886b67aff6e103f251d752dc","tid":1373183,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:49:03.000Z","msg":"支持 推"},{"pid":"617729261a0a9fd1f14726590d373da614ed123d","tid":1373183,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:49:52.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記我地入元朗既目標<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0b33acbd5286314f76e57f469e22095e9655ed34","tid":1373183,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"其實冇人知前線決定左乜，講真消息傳唔到<br />\n<br />\n今日聽到1930退，其實都已經好多人問，怕假傳聖旨"},{"pid":"1c5dd2e85534b2e7bb99d033904d3798d35ef03e","tid":1373183,"uid":284383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:50:47.000Z","msg":"721發夢又係咁<br />\n成日掉低前線班手足"},{"pid":"4aa539c0aea4edb8c03258cf13a33ff838710d2b","tid":1373183,"uid":158977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:51:04.000Z","msg":"點解我聽到嘅野同你唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係唔退嗰啲人嚟 <br />\n我幾乎次次都係聽到開mic話<br />\n&ldquo;前線決定退啦&rdquo; 或者 <br />\n&ldquo;我地退後啲先 比前線有位退&rdquo;<br />\n先會大部分人退"},{"pid":"4ffedf87bf4d46bc3078587840d9a583ab0ef9fe","tid":1